title: Matchsafe
creditline: Gift of Stephen W. Brener and Carol B. Brener
description: Figure of man seated wearing Near Eastern outfit with green coat, short yellow pants with green stripes and white waistcoat with red decoration and light blue buttons. Figure smokes a long narrow orange colored pipe. Figure wears a turban on head.

Matchsafe.
